model1 <- function(a, data) {
  a[1] + data$x * a[2]
}

model1(c(5,5), sim1)

9 Root-mean-squared deviation

measure_dist <- function(mod, data) {
  diff <- data$y - model1(mod, data)
  diff^2 %>%
    mean() %>%
    sqrt()
}
measure_dist(c(5,5), sim1)
## [1] 19.10774

11 Prime Find Func

primary <- function(x) {
  if (min(x %% 2:(x-1)) > 0) {
    return(x)
  }else{
    return(0)
  }
}

array = c(1:1000)

primeArray <- matrix()

count = 0

for (x in array) {
  if (x == 1) {
    next
  }
  if (primary(x) > 0) {
    primeArray <- append(primeArray, x)
    count = count + 1
  }
  
}
primeArray <- primeArray[!is.na(primeArray)]
count
